    "Based on the results of the secondary analysis, I will then derive precise definitions for CEXs and DEXs, using the newly gained insights and the underlying rationale of these dimensions within the CEX and DEX research landscape.",
    "Looking at CEXs and DEXs from a technological perspective, there are distinct features and characteristics that set these two approaches apart.",
    "CEXs provide an easy-touse, centralized platform for cryptocurrency trading.",
